  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1998-07-16", 
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a limited credit for qualified contributions made for the construction and renovation of public high schools in a limited number of designated high school districts which meet specified criteria, including that there is a poverty rate of at least 45 percent and a per capita income of $9,000 or less in the district's municipality."
